descriptionHtml:
ENBseries.ini for ENBv262

V1-------
Saturation enhanced. 
Working towards vanilla style.
enbseries.ini is now closer to complete.
enbeffect.fx used for additional saturation.
saturationboost.esp for maximum saturation in most scenes.  Will likely cause CTD with other lighting mods.

Install:
step 1; Download and install ENB v0.262 from ENBdev.com(Documented install instruction available at ENBdev.com)
step 2; (back-up)Copy and overwrite enbseries.ini and [Enbseries]enbeffect.fx.ini
Optional 3;  Extract and put in [Data]saturationboost.esp
 
Uninstall instructions at ENBdev.com

V1-------Old
Graphical enhancement to Skyrim.  
Balanced vanilla style.  
Couldn't find an ENB to my liking...created to make my Heroine Suit even more shiny, with effects from ENB.  
Mid-high performance impact.
